WEBVTT

01:39.430 --> 01:43.330
[Road to Success]

01:44.750 --> 01:47.729
[Episode 32]

01:50.150 --> 01:50.840
I'm sorry.

01:51.479 --> 01:53.080
I can accept any punishment,

01:53.789 --> 01:55.920
and I can also withdraw from the match.

01:55.920 --> 01:57.920
But I don't want my personal matters

01:58.350 --> 01:59.410
to affect Hengjiu.

02:05.280 --> 02:07.080
Do you have any other questions?

02:10.000 --> 02:12.400
About this, you can decide for yourselves.

02:15.280 --> 02:17.000
Ms. Lin, Coach.

02:18.520 --> 02:19.920
We want to take some time
to think it over.

02:19.920 --> 02:20.579
No problem.

02:21.630 --> 02:22.190
Let's go.

02:25.000 --> 02:26.000
I'll take him out first.

02:26.000 --> 02:27.630
Let me know when you've made a decision.

02:27.630 --> 02:28.870
-Okay.
-Okay.

02:30.610 --> 02:31.610
Let's go.

02:42.560 --> 02:43.750
I don't get it.

02:43.750 --> 02:45.020
He's the one who did something wrong.

02:45.020 --> 02:46.450
What is there for us to consider?

02:46.450 --> 02:47.680
Wrong is wrong.

02:48.240 --> 02:49.640
I know what you guys mean.

02:49.800 --> 02:52.560
But I think we should
treat different things separately.

02:52.560 --> 02:54.540
Besides, he's our opponent.

02:54.560 --> 02:56.160
Don't act like a saint, okay?

02:56.840 --> 02:58.690
He was shedding tears just now.

02:58.720 --> 03:00.450
Who knows if he was just acting?

03:00.460 --> 03:02.190
He just wanted us to forgive him

03:02.210 --> 03:03.940
and pretend nothing happened.

03:04.750 --> 03:05.910
If we report him,

03:06.430 --> 03:07.790
what will be the consequences?

03:07.790 --> 03:10.190
This could affect him
for the rest of his life.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.800
I think we should give him a chance.

03:11.800 --> 03:13.120
If we give him a chance,

03:13.120 --> 03:14.850
who's going to give us a chance?

03:15.750 --> 03:16.280
Fu,

03:16.840 --> 03:17.590
if Hengjiu loses him,

03:17.590 --> 03:19.990
our chances of winning
will be much higher.

03:20.030 --> 03:20.590
Right.

03:23.360 --> 03:25.420
Have you all forgotten what you said?

03:26.150 --> 03:28.560
We play football to win.

03:33.190 --> 03:33.840
Everyone,

03:34.280 --> 03:36.120
do you remember what Director Qian said?

03:36.120 --> 03:37.910
We are about
to take the college entrance exam.

03:37.910 --> 03:39.190
As long as we beat Hengjiu,

03:39.190 --> 03:41.520
we'll have a chance at special admission.

03:48.800 --> 03:49.360
Qin,

03:50.190 --> 03:51.190
what do you think?

03:54.280 --> 03:55.930
I don't know what to say.

03:57.670 --> 03:59.150
But if I had to say,

04:00.000 --> 04:01.000
I think...

04:02.000 --> 04:04.660
I still want to beat that Qin Qiechu
on the field.

04:05.360 --> 04:07.010
He slapped us in the face,

04:07.040 --> 04:08.810
so we have to hit back, right?

04:09.400 --> 04:10.210
Come on.

04:10.870 --> 04:12.030
Is there something wrong with your brain?

04:12.030 --> 04:13.030
Are you talking to me?

04:13.030 --> 04:13.870
Isn't there?

04:14.080 --> 04:15.870
This match is related to our future.

04:15.870 --> 04:16.600
If you don't want to go to college,

04:16.600 --> 04:18.240
could you please not drag us down?

04:18.240 --> 04:19.480
I drag you down?

04:19.720 --> 04:20.390
I'll say it one last time.

04:20.390 --> 04:21.160
Listen carefully.

04:21.160 --> 04:24.510
With your terrible grades,
do you even need me to drag you down?

04:24.510 --> 04:26.720
-Enough!
-Alright, alright!

04:26.720 --> 04:28.800
You're desperate to go to college, huh?

04:28.800 --> 04:29.710
Qin Ao.

04:29.830 --> 04:31.890
-Alright, alright.
-Don't touch me!

04:39.680 --> 04:40.430
How about...

04:40.830 --> 04:42.720
we use Robert's Rules of Order?

04:43.430 --> 04:44.190
I agree.

04:44.830 --> 04:45.830
What do you think?

04:52.830 --> 04:53.510
Alright.

04:53.510 --> 04:54.640
Let's start voting.

05:00.550 --> 05:01.670
For those who think

05:02.190 --> 05:03.390
we should report him,

05:03.630 --> 05:04.690
stand on this side.

05:05.340 --> 05:06.560
For those who think we should let it go,

05:06.560 --> 05:07.620
stand on this side.

05:26.380 --> 05:28.110
Do you want to sit down and wait?

05:39.200 --> 05:41.010
Coach, Ms. Lin.

05:43.390 --> 05:45.190
-I…
-Have you made up your minds?

05:46.600 --> 05:47.840
You guys talk.

05:48.240 --> 05:48.870
Okay.

05:51.480 --> 05:52.400
Come in with me.

06:13.870 --> 06:15.790
Is it true that no matter the outcome,

06:15.790 --> 06:16.790
you can accept it?

06:17.950 --> 06:19.610
Given the current situation,

06:19.930 --> 06:21.610
it's not really up to me, is it?

06:21.680 --> 06:22.270
Yes.

06:42.420 --> 06:43.770
By a vote of 9 to 2,

06:44.190 --> 06:45.480
we decided not to report you

06:45.480 --> 06:46.540
or call the police.

06:49.790 --> 06:50.880
You can go now.

06:53.080 --> 06:54.130
Why?

06:54.470 --> 06:55.310
Did you think

06:55.310 --> 06:57.110
we would definitely report you?

06:57.270 --> 06:58.000
I know.

06:58.310 --> 07:00.090
Even though
you didn't want us to report you,

07:00.090 --> 07:01.690
deep down,

07:01.950 --> 07:03.000
you probably didn't believe

07:03.000 --> 07:04.800
we'd give up this chance.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.110
Alright.

07:08.110 --> 07:09.130
I'll be blunt.

07:09.360 --> 07:10.360
We do want to win,

07:10.610 --> 07:12.540
but we want to beat you on the field.

07:13.000 --> 07:13.590
Also,

07:14.240 --> 07:16.120
that brat Qin Qiechu

07:16.120 --> 07:17.820
has always been talking about us
behind our backs.

07:17.820 --> 07:20.080
We've wanted to crush him for a long time.

07:21.360 --> 07:23.600
Just like that,
the special admission spots are gone.

07:23.600 --> 07:25.530
So you guys better not go easy on us.

07:25.920 --> 07:27.430
Or I'll regret it to death.

07:29.860 --> 07:31.620
Now do you know why?

07:34.159 --> 07:35.000
Thank you.

07:37.240 --> 07:38.390
I'll give it my all.

07:44.890 --> 07:45.520
Right,

07:45.550 --> 07:47.390
don't forget to sign the IOU.

07:47.630 --> 07:49.120
This isn't a gift from me.

07:54.630 --> 07:56.620
[IOU] [Debtor: Fang Sulun]

07:58.830 --> 07:59.560
Keep it safe.

08:02.790 --> 08:03.590
Here.

08:03.990 --> 08:04.650
It's yours.

08:08.490 --> 08:09.420
Thank you,

08:09.620 --> 08:10.500
Lin Lu.

08:15.160 --> 08:15.960
What's wrong?

08:16.360 --> 08:17.480
I'm so proud.

08:19.950 --> 08:20.720
I know.

08:21.560 --> 08:22.190
Me too.

08:23.720 --> 08:25.360
They've really grown up.

08:28.050 --> 08:29.230
Then I'll...

08:29.720 --> 08:30.510
see you on the field.

08:30.510 --> 08:33.240
-Of course we will.
-See you on the field.

08:33.240 --> 08:34.370
See you on the field.

08:35.289 --> 08:37.520
Tell that brat Qin Qiechu

08:37.909 --> 08:39.270
to rest well today.

08:39.270 --> 08:41.929
He might get knocked flat
on the field tomorrow!

08:43.150 --> 08:44.720
Okay, I'll pass it on.

08:45.480 --> 08:46.910
Be careful.
You may get crushed by us then.

08:46.910 --> 08:47.930
They definitely will.

08:47.930 --> 08:50.150
-They definitely will be crushed by us.
-I told you we would do our best,

08:50.150 --> 08:51.320
so we definitely will.

08:51.320 --> 08:52.120
Okay, okay.

08:55.870 --> 08:57.790
This is the second clash
between Yongchuan Hengjiu

08:57.620 --> 08:59.680
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League
No. 8 High School vs. Hengjiu]

08:57.790 --> 08:59.000
and Hongjing No. 8 High School.

08:59.000 --> 09:00.550
Who will be the champion?

09:00.550 --> 09:01.960
We'll soon find out.

09:02.510 --> 09:04.720
Both cheer squads are full of energy.

09:03.460 --> 09:05.440
[LIVE]
[Hongjing No. 8 High][Yongchuan Hengjiu]

09:04.720 --> 09:05.750
I believe this match

09:05.530 --> 09:07.490
[Commentator]

09:05.750 --> 09:07.780
will definitely not disappoint
the audience.

09:07.780 --> 09:10.340
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team]

09:11.000 --> 09:12.870
This is the 2nd clash
between the two teams.

09:12.700 --> 09:13.950
[Victory for Hongjing]

09:12.870 --> 09:15.200
Will Hongjing No. 8 High School
go all the way,

09:14.020 --> 09:14.940
[Hold Your Head High, Hongjing's Pride]

09:15.200 --> 09:17.670
or will Yongchuan Hengjiu
be crowned champions for the 6th time?

09:17.670 --> 09:20.280
We'll find out in 90 minutes.

09:20.360 --> 09:22.510
Both cheer squads are full of energy.

09:22.510 --> 09:23.630
I believe this match

09:23.630 --> 09:24.960
will definitely not disappoint

09:24.960 --> 09:27.360
the audience here and in front of the TV.

09:29.470 --> 09:30.980
Yongchuan Hengjiu!

09:29.790 --> 09:30.710
[Invincible Yongchuan Hengjiu]

09:31.150 --> 09:33.960
-Go for it!
-Go for it!

09:34.240 --> 09:35.750
Hongjing, Hongjing!

09:35.750 --> 09:37.360
Champions of the universe!

09:37.360 --> 09:38.720
No. 8 High School

09:38.720 --> 09:40.270
rules the field!

09:40.270 --> 09:41.270
Go, go, go!

09:40.510 --> 09:42.350
[VIP]

09:42.550 --> 09:44.550
Father-in-law, this is Hengjiu's VIP area.

09:44.550 --> 09:46.080
What are you doing?

09:46.080 --> 09:46.840
So what?

09:46.840 --> 09:48.550
I'm a hardcore fan of Hongjing.

09:48.550 --> 09:49.350
What's wrong?

09:49.540 --> 09:50.070
Oh, wait.

09:50.750 --> 09:52.480
Who are you calling father-in-law?

09:52.480 --> 09:53.910
You are the chairman of Hengjiu.

09:53.910 --> 09:54.910
It doesn't look good.

09:54.910 --> 09:55.910
-It's not appropriate.
-Yeah.

09:55.910 --> 09:57.680
Right, it's not appropriate.

09:58.910 --> 10:00.360
I'll go over to Hongjing's side.

10:00.360 --> 10:01.720
Restrain yourself.

10:02.600 --> 10:04.730
Come on, honey. Don't leave me behind.

10:04.790 --> 10:06.530
-Honey.
-What are you doing here?

10:06.530 --> 10:08.150
We each support one side.

10:08.150 --> 10:09.320
You support our daughter,

10:09.320 --> 10:10.910
and I'll support our son's team.

10:10.910 --> 10:11.630
Mom. Mom.

10:12.480 --> 10:14.480
Take your lovestruck husband away.

10:14.750 --> 10:15.790
Look at him.

10:15.790 --> 10:17.920
He is here, but his heart is over there.

10:18.080 --> 10:20.750
I'm afraid
he'll ruin Hengjiu's team spirit.

10:21.120 --> 10:22.250
Listen to your tone.

10:22.550 --> 10:23.120
Honey,

10:23.120 --> 10:24.000
I'll go with you.

10:24.000 --> 10:24.440
Be careful.

10:24.440 --> 10:25.440
I'll go with you.

10:31.240 --> 10:33.700
I won't. I absolutely won't...

10:34.840 --> 10:36.380
I will definitely stand firm

10:36.380 --> 10:37.640
for you.

10:37.820 --> 10:38.630
[Invincible Yongchuan Hengjiu]

10:38.750 --> 10:40.320
Come on, Hengjiu!

10:39.440 --> 10:40.350
[Invincible Yongchuan Hengjiu]

10:40.600 --> 10:42.630
Go, go, go!

10:42.630 --> 10:44.030
Come on, Hengjiu!

10:43.420 --> 10:44.390
[Invincible Yongchuan Hengjiu]

10:44.030 --> 10:46.240
-Come on, Hengjiu!
-Go, go, go!

10:46.240 --> 10:47.630
Hongjing No. 8 High!

10:47.630 --> 10:50.790
Go, go, go!

10:50.810 --> 10:52.790
Is there anyone you particularly want
to cheer for today?

10:52.790 --> 10:54.060
It must be Qin Ao.

10:54.090 --> 10:55.360
-No! That's not true!
-Of course it's him.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.440
You're blushing.

10:56.440 --> 10:57.380
No, I'm not.

10:57.630 --> 10:59.730
Miss, can we switch seats?

11:00.120 --> 11:00.750
Sure.

11:00.750 --> 11:01.800
Great. Here.

11:01.170 --> 11:03.090
[Go For It]

11:02.240 --> 11:03.300
And this one.

11:03.970 --> 11:05.380
[Hold Your Head High, Hongjing's Pride]

11:06.840 --> 11:09.780
[Victory for Hongjing]

11:09.120 --> 11:09.960
Qi Liang's dad,

11:09.960 --> 11:11.360
you said you weren't coming.

11:11.360 --> 11:12.600
Look at how great the kids are.

11:12.600 --> 11:13.240
Yeah.

11:13.240 --> 11:15.600
It's a good thing
that they were given this chance.

11:15.600 --> 11:16.230
Later,

11:16.230 --> 11:18.080
just cheer for them with all your might.

11:18.080 --> 11:20.030
-Yeah.
-Yeah. Cheer for them with all your might.

11:20.030 --> 11:21.270
Okay! Come on!

11:22.240 --> 11:23.840
Hongjing No. 8 High!

11:23.840 --> 11:25.870
Go, go, go!

11:25.870 --> 11:27.600
Hongjing No. 8 High!

11:27.600 --> 11:30.120
Go, go, go!

11:32.000 --> 11:34.000
Director Jin, what brings you here?

11:34.120 --> 11:35.450
Isn't this a school-wide event?

11:35.450 --> 11:36.630
What's wrong with me being here?

11:36.630 --> 11:37.630
You should have come earlier. Come on.

11:37.630 --> 11:39.030
Have a seat. Here's a flag.

11:39.030 --> 11:40.270
Come.

11:40.320 --> 11:42.730
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

11:42.850 --> 11:44.540
[Yongchuan Hengjiu]

11:59.300 --> 12:00.690
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

12:00.720 --> 12:02.370
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
vs. Yongchuan Hengjiu]

12:01.220 --> 12:04.510
-Hongjing No. 8 High!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:04.510 --> 12:07.960
-Hongjing No. 8 High!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:12.510 --> 12:15.320
Don't expect our team to go easy today.

12:16.860 --> 12:18.120
It's a battle of honor.

12:18.360 --> 12:19.080
Likewise.

12:20.000 --> 12:21.320
A battle of honor?

12:21.320 --> 12:23.050
You guys will definitely lose.

12:23.120 --> 12:24.510
Are you so confident

12:24.510 --> 12:26.040
because of the lace collar?

12:45.120 --> 12:45.960
Baby, hi.

12:47.320 --> 12:48.360
Where are those kids?

12:48.360 --> 12:49.120
Call them over.

12:49.120 --> 12:50.320
I want to talk to them.

12:50.670 --> 12:52.410
Ms. Ju is here to cheer for you.

12:52.910 --> 12:53.480
-Let's go.
-Okay.

12:53.480 --> 12:54.390
It's Ms. Ju.

12:54.630 --> 12:55.320
Ms. Ju.

12:55.320 --> 12:55.910
Ms. Ju.

12:57.720 --> 12:59.840
-Ms. Ju.
-Ms. Ju.

12:59.840 --> 13:02.240
I have a performance today,

13:02.240 --> 13:03.000
so I can't come to the game

13:03.000 --> 13:05.480
to cheer you on.

13:05.790 --> 13:07.240
But you must win

13:07.240 --> 13:09.120
and make us proud, understand?

13:09.120 --> 13:10.890
Otherwise...

13:10.660 --> 13:14.290
[Microphone on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

13:11.120 --> 13:12.630
5 physics papers.

13:14.840 --> 13:16.200
Seriously? Come on!

13:16.200 --> 13:17.750
Then 10.

13:19.080 --> 13:20.480
-This is too much pressure.
-How can you do this?

13:20.480 --> 13:21.480
-How can you do this?
-That's lame.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.750
-Alright. That's enough.
-It's not fun at all.

13:22.750 --> 13:23.720
Let's get ready.

13:23.720 --> 13:24.600
Brothers,

13:24.600 --> 13:26.480
let's play to our heart's content!

13:26.480 --> 13:28.390
-To our heart's content!
-To our heart's content!

13:28.390 --> 13:29.600
Wanxing, go ahead.

13:29.600 --> 13:31.550
Go for it!

13:31.550 --> 13:32.550
Don't worry, Li.

13:32.550 --> 13:33.960
Wait for our good news.

13:34.600 --> 13:35.480
We need a little ritual.

13:35.480 --> 13:36.280
Come on, come on.

13:36.280 --> 13:37.670
Come on, come on!

13:37.670 --> 13:38.210
Captain.

13:38.510 --> 13:40.480
-Coach, Coach. Ms. Lin.
-Coach.

13:40.870 --> 13:42.120
Hongjing No. 8 High!

13:42.120 --> 13:44.600
Let's go for it!

13:45.030 --> 13:46.000
If you ask me,

13:46.000 --> 13:47.870
the Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team

13:47.870 --> 13:49.240
will lose no matter who

13:49.240 --> 13:50.390
their coach is.

13:52.600 --> 13:54.380
Hongjing is a respectable opponent.

13:54.380 --> 13:55.600
We shouldn't underestimate them.

13:55.600 --> 13:56.510
What happened?

13:56.510 --> 13:58.710
Why the 180-degree change in attitude?

13:59.230 --> 14:00.890
They deserve to be respected.

14:01.040 --> 14:01.910
Let's go all out!

14:01.910 --> 14:02.370
Come on!

14:04.600 --> 14:05.730
Yongchuan Hengjiu!

14:06.480 --> 14:07.480
We've got this!

14:08.200 --> 14:10.360
Now it's time for the coin toss.

14:10.360 --> 14:11.870
As the referee tosses the coin,

14:11.870 --> 14:13.960
the final officially begins.

14:13.960 --> 14:16.000
Hongjing No. 8 High
and Yongchuan Hengjiu

14:16.000 --> 14:17.960
have fought their way
from the group stage to the final.

14:17.960 --> 14:20.390
Today they'll finally
face each other again.

14:20.390 --> 14:21.750
It's a clash of old rivals.

14:21.750 --> 14:22.440
This match

14:22.440 --> 14:24.120
is destined to be a thrilling encounter.

14:24.120 --> 14:26.120
Let's focus on the field

14:26.120 --> 14:28.030
and witness the crowning
of the champion together.

14:28.030 --> 14:30.580
Yongchuan, Yongchuan, march on to glory!

14:30.610 --> 14:34.270
Yongchuan, Yongchuan, march on to glory!

14:34.270 --> 14:37.940
Hongjing, Hongjing, make history!

14:37.970 --> 14:40.840
Hongjing, Hongjing, make history!

14:40.840 --> 14:43.200
Hengjiu's captain,
No. 7 Fang Sulun, kicks off.

14:43.200 --> 14:45.080
He passes to No. 10, Qin Qiechu.

14:45.080 --> 14:47.120
Qin Qiechu beats three players in a row!

14:47.120 --> 14:48.440
He reaches the edge of the box!

14:48.440 --> 14:50.320
But the ball is intercepted

14:50.320 --> 14:51.320
by Zheng Ren, Hongjing's No. 5.

14:51.320 --> 14:52.320
He dribbles the ball

14:52.320 --> 14:53.440
and moves forward.

15:01.120 --> 15:01.910
Ms. Lin!

15:02.630 --> 15:04.430
We didn't win the championship.

15:04.600 --> 15:05.730
We will always be...

15:07.120 --> 15:07.850
runners-up.

15:09.150 --> 15:10.600
Lin Lu, you smart kid.

15:11.240 --> 15:12.800
I hope this time,

15:13.080 --> 15:14.810
you won't finish second again.

15:22.670 --> 15:23.480
Feng Suo.

15:24.000 --> 15:24.660
♪ A starlit night ♪

15:24.150 --> 15:25.500
You are always the team's

15:25.500 --> 15:27.380
most solid last line of defense.

15:25.890 --> 15:29.670
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

15:27.720 --> 15:28.800
Jianghe!

15:31.100 --> 15:32.160
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

15:33.100 --> 15:36.750
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

15:38.150 --> 15:39.170
♪ Lasting memories ♪

15:40.390 --> 15:44.460
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

15:43.000 --> 15:43.910
Hey.

15:43.910 --> 15:46.750
Don't you need to get a teacher's
permission to borrow a football?

15:45.220 --> 15:46.210
♪ To run toward you ♪

15:46.870 --> 15:48.620
What grade and class are you in?

15:47.030 --> 15:51.310
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

15:48.790 --> 15:49.790
What's your name?

15:49.840 --> 15:51.650
I'm a senior in Class 5.
My name is Qin Ao.

15:51.650 --> 15:52.840
Qin as in Emperor Qin.

15:52.730 --> 15:55.510
[100 free football equipment rentals]

15:52.840 --> 15:55.020
Ao as in Tibetan Mastiff,
without the "dog" component.

15:55.020 --> 15:56.050
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

15:55.080 --> 15:55.750
This works.

15:56.030 --> 15:57.000
I'll lend you the ball.

15:57.000 --> 15:57.670
Really?

15:57.350 --> 15:58.580
♪ Because you're with me ♪

15:58.440 --> 15:59.640
Then who will sign it?

16:01.670 --> 16:03.070
It's fine. Again!

16:01.830 --> 16:02.890
♪ The light shimmers ♪

16:04.530 --> 16:05.450
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

16:05.320 --> 16:06.240
Chen Jianghe.

16:06.910 --> 16:08.000
Your hard work

16:07.210 --> 16:08.150
♪ Running towards you ♪

16:08.320 --> 16:10.280
makes the 100-use ball borrowing card

16:09.050 --> 16:10.270
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

16:10.570 --> 16:11.930
seem far from enough.

16:14.500 --> 16:15.280
♪ Walk side by side ♪

16:16.130 --> 16:17.740
♪ Become ourselves ♪

16:16.750 --> 16:17.280
Let's go!

16:19.270 --> 16:19.730
Come on!

16:20.280 --> 16:20.890
♪ Amid the storm ♪

16:22.060 --> 16:26.170
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

16:22.870 --> 16:23.270
There!

16:25.440 --> 16:26.960
-Go, go, go!
-Okay!

16:27.110 --> 16:28.190
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

16:29.270 --> 16:33.150
♪ A chemistry about to emerge ♪

16:34.460 --> 16:35.300
♪ The stars are shining ♪

16:36.180 --> 16:40.630
♪ Take my hand and run forward ♪

16:37.320 --> 16:38.040
Pass it now!

16:38.750 --> 16:41.080
The person we've been waiting for is here.

16:41.120 --> 16:42.670
A bunch of amateurs.

16:41.480 --> 16:42.160
♪ For you ♪

16:42.670 --> 16:44.240
You call yourselves football players?

16:43.260 --> 16:47.600
♪ I'm willing to
keep practicing and practicing ♪

16:44.240 --> 16:45.310
Get out of here.

16:46.070 --> 16:46.910
Am I wrong?

16:47.600 --> 16:48.790
A bunch of losers.

16:49.180 --> 16:50.070
Wen Chengye.

16:50.630 --> 16:51.750
Has it been a long time

16:51.350 --> 16:52.740
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

16:52.000 --> 16:53.670
since you felt lonely?

16:53.670 --> 16:54.390
Dad.

16:53.810 --> 16:55.030
♪ Because you're with me ♪

16:54.870 --> 16:55.930
I'm not a stray dog.

16:56.510 --> 16:57.510
I've got friends.

16:58.290 --> 16:59.350
♪ The light shimmers ♪

17:00.720 --> 17:02.640
I know what I want to study.

17:00.990 --> 17:01.900
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

17:02.840 --> 17:03.510
Football—

17:03.660 --> 17:04.599
♪ Running towards you ♪

17:04.440 --> 17:05.960
I will keep playing it.

17:05.500 --> 17:06.720
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

17:10.960 --> 17:11.730
♪ Walk side by side ♪

17:12.579 --> 17:14.190
♪ Become ourselves ♪

17:13.589 --> 17:15.510
And you, Fu Xinshu.

17:16.790 --> 17:17.510
Ms. Lin,

17:18.400 --> 17:19.670
I don't have

17:20.440 --> 17:22.200
many chances left in this life.

17:23.890 --> 17:25.270
I really love football.

17:26.589 --> 17:28.000
So I don't want to give up.

17:33.000 --> 17:34.640
You truly deserve to be

17:35.480 --> 17:37.410
the captain of Hongjing No. 8 High.

17:46.260 --> 17:47.310
The 23rd!

17:51.400 --> 17:52.240
Qin Ao!

17:54.830 --> 17:57.090
Only those who have traveled far and wide

17:57.350 --> 18:00.720
will reach the hardest stretch
of the journey.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.750
You know very well

18:03.860 --> 18:04.790
♪ Regaining courage ♪

18:05.200 --> 18:06.460
that sometimes taking a step back

18:06.460 --> 18:07.520
♪ Because you're with me ♪

18:06.830 --> 18:08.440
can make the journey easier.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.370
But when the coin is tossed

18:11.050 --> 18:12.100
♪ Heartbeat's response ♪

18:12.830 --> 18:14.160
and the bell rings,

18:13.750 --> 18:14.660
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

18:16.350 --> 18:19.550
you will still find yourself
trapped on this narrow path.

18:20.880 --> 18:21.550
Because

18:22.750 --> 18:24.750
those who truly walk the narrow path

18:28.510 --> 18:30.070
will never give up.

18:39.320 --> 18:40.250
♪ Regaining courage ♪

18:40.160 --> 18:41.040
Behind you!

18:41.900 --> 18:42.900
♪ Because you're with me ♪

18:43.160 --> 18:44.880
Hengjiu's captain, Fang Sulun,

18:44.880 --> 18:46.500
passes the ball into the attacking half!

18:46.500 --> 18:47.510
♪ Heartbeat's response ♪

18:46.750 --> 18:48.550
Qin Qiechu takes possession
and breaks into the box!

18:48.550 --> 18:51.010
Hongjing is in danger. He goes down!

18:48.690 --> 18:49.810
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

18:51.510 --> 18:52.640
-Here!
-Penalty!

18:52.640 --> 18:54.590
The referee points to the penalty spot!

18:54.590 --> 18:55.000
Okay.

18:55.000 --> 18:56.800
That shouldn't have been a foul.

18:57.960 --> 18:59.440
-Hongjing's defense is caught out
-Okay.

18:59.440 --> 19:00.440
and forced to commit a foul.

19:00.440 --> 19:02.920
The referee awards Hengjiu a penalty.

19:04.740 --> 19:06.510
The match has reached a critical moment.

19:06.510 --> 19:07.160
Hengjiu

19:07.160 --> 19:10.820
have been given a penalty
that could change the course of the game.

19:12.720 --> 19:14.070
Standing over the spot

19:14.070 --> 19:15.960
is Hengjiu's star player,

19:15.960 --> 19:16.870
Qin Qiechu.

19:17.000 --> 19:17.680
Facing him

19:17.680 --> 19:20.270
is Hongjing's goalkeeper, Feng Suo.

19:20.270 --> 19:21.240
At this moment,

19:21.240 --> 19:22.510
the weight of the match rests squarely

19:22.510 --> 19:24.970
on the shoulders
of these two young players.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.590
I don't believe he'll score!

19:31.960 --> 19:32.680
Suo,

19:33.160 --> 19:34.420
we're counting on you.

19:35.070 --> 19:36.130
It doesn't matter if he scores.

19:36.130 --> 19:37.070
We've still got time

19:37.070 --> 19:38.330
to turn things around.

19:44.750 --> 19:45.400
Stay calm.

19:46.000 --> 19:47.310
Just like in training.

19:47.790 --> 19:48.760
I can do this.

19:51.070 --> 19:52.870
Trust your instincts, Feng Suo.

19:53.590 --> 19:55.990
You've practiced this thousands of times.

20:08.000 --> 20:08.720
Coach,

20:08.970 --> 20:11.340
how do I save a penalty kick?

20:12.510 --> 20:15.050
You must believe you'll save it

20:15.350 --> 20:18.080
more than your opponent believes
they'll score.

20:18.160 --> 20:19.220
Forget everything

20:20.000 --> 20:21.640
and bravely dive to one side!

20:24.790 --> 20:26.160
What a save!

20:26.160 --> 20:28.200
Feng Suo saves Qin Qiechu's penalty

20:28.200 --> 20:29.800
and gathers the ball safely!

20:29.880 --> 20:31.640
Under the immense pressure of the final,

20:31.640 --> 20:35.000
Feng Suo makes a priceless save.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.920
The score is still 0-0.

20:36.920 --> 20:39.070
Both sides are still evenly matched.

20:39.960 --> 20:40.750
Come on!

20:57.580 --> 20:58.290
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team]

20:58.380 --> 21:00.030
[VIP]

21:01.040 --> 21:01.680
[Come On!]

21:03.010 --> 21:04.150
[Hold Your Head High, Hongjing's Pride]

21:20.350 --> 21:22.720
The match is now in the 88th minute.

21:22.720 --> 21:25.200
Hongjing No. 8 High earns a corner kick.

21:25.200 --> 21:28.060
It will be taken by their captain,
No. 10, Fu Xinshu.

21:45.920 --> 21:47.320
The corner kick is taken.

21:51.720 --> 21:53.440
There's chaos in the box.

21:53.440 --> 21:55.970
Qin Ao gets to the ball first!
A header on goal!

21:56.030 --> 21:58.030
Hengjiu's goalkeeper parries the ball,

21:58.030 --> 22:00.030
but the danger isn't over yet!

22:02.160 --> 22:03.310
No. 11!

22:05.440 --> 22:07.920
No. 11, Wen Chengye,
follows up with a shot!

22:10.790 --> 22:12.440
Goal!

22:17.430 --> 22:18.860
[Victory for Hongjing]

22:18.900 --> 22:21.640
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

22:18.910 --> 22:19.680
[Hongjing No. 8 High School,
Strong as a Dragon]

22:22.990 --> 22:25.020
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

22:25.680 --> 22:27.350
The game is over!

22:26.820 --> 22:27.700
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

22:27.350 --> 22:29.710
Hongjing No. 8 High are the champions!

22:28.690 --> 22:29.910
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

22:30.590 --> 22:32.240
I think the charm of competitive sports

22:31.180 --> 22:33.220
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

22:32.240 --> 22:34.480
lies in the fact
that everything is unknown.

22:34.380 --> 22:37.190
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

22:34.960 --> 22:38.160
True warriors don't run on a smooth road,

22:38.160 --> 22:40.700
but break through the narrow paths.

22:38.340 --> 22:40.480
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

22:41.510 --> 22:42.440
Dear audience,

22:42.260 --> 22:43.820
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

22:42.440 --> 22:44.880
let's remember the names
of these young men.

22:44.780 --> 22:45.920
♪ Thrive and bloom ♪

22:44.880 --> 22:45.720
They are:

22:45.720 --> 22:47.590
No. 11, Wen Chengye,

22:45.940 --> 22:46.780
[Come On!]

22:46.790 --> 22:49.730
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

22:47.590 --> 22:49.420
No. 10, Fu Xinshu,

22:49.750 --> 22:51.160
No. 9, Qin Ao,

22:50.650 --> 22:53.550
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

22:51.310 --> 22:53.080
No. 7, Chen Jianghe,

22:51.660 --> 22:51.850
[Go For It]

22:53.240 --> 22:54.840
No. 6, Lin Lu,

22:54.860 --> 22:56.660
No. 13, Zheng Feiyang,

22:57.200 --> 22:58.870
No. 18, Qi Liang,

22:59.110 --> 23:01.100
No. 23, Zhi Hui,

23:01.350 --> 23:03.090
No. 1, Feng Suo,

23:03.200 --> 23:04.960
No. 5, Yu Ming,

23:04.960 --> 23:06.550
and No. 15, Zheng Ren!

23:07.220 --> 23:09.980
♪ If braving the wind
and waves ♪

23:07.310 --> 23:09.350
They didn't retreat on the narrow paths,

23:09.350 --> 23:11.110
didn't fall apart in adversity,

23:10.890 --> 23:14.200
♪ Is what it takes to grow ♪

23:11.110 --> 23:13.040
and didn't collapse under doubts.

23:13.110 --> 23:14.830
This is their

23:14.830 --> 23:16.040
sportsmanship!

23:14.980 --> 23:17.610
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

23:16.830 --> 23:17.790
Everyone,

23:17.790 --> 23:19.720
let's meet again next year

23:18.520 --> 23:21.440
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

23:19.720 --> 23:21.960
for another brilliant moment!

23:22.240 --> 23:25.450
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

23:26.290 --> 23:28.610
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

23:28.590 --> 23:32.030
[One Year Later]

23:30.410 --> 23:31.600
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

23:32.340 --> 23:33.890
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

23:33.240 --> 23:34.370
We're almost there.

23:34.780 --> 23:37.300
[Sports Equipment Room]

23:34.830 --> 23:35.550
-Hello, Director.
-Hello, Director.

23:35.550 --> 23:36.270
Hello.

23:45.480 --> 23:46.880
Come and take a look.

23:47.650 --> 23:50.410
This is our sports equipment room.

23:52.920 --> 23:54.160
Here are the keys.

23:54.160 --> 23:54.750
Okay.

23:54.750 --> 23:55.750
This is your desk.

23:58.160 --> 23:59.020
Director Qian.

23:59.350 --> 24:01.550
I heard that the previous keeper

24:01.550 --> 24:04.200
was a woman who was the top student
at Yongchuan University.

24:04.200 --> 24:06.030
I heard during her tenure,

24:06.030 --> 24:07.070
not only did she lead our

24:07.070 --> 24:09.070
Hongjing Football Team
to the top of the league table,

24:09.070 --> 24:10.310
but now she's also applying for a Ph.D.

24:10.310 --> 24:11.400
That shows

24:11.720 --> 24:14.000
our sports equipment room

24:14.000 --> 24:15.480
is a lucky place.

24:17.070 --> 24:18.270
I wouldn't

24:18.270 --> 24:19.750
bring just anyone here.

24:21.200 --> 24:21.880
Okay, Director.

24:21.880 --> 24:23.480
I will definitely work hard.

24:24.350 --> 24:26.750
Alright, this is the rack for volleyballs.

24:27.000 --> 24:28.750
And this shelf is all shuttlecocks.

24:28.750 --> 24:29.950
Let's look over here.

24:31.070 --> 24:32.830
-This is...
-This is the equipment supply room.

24:32.830 --> 24:33.360
Alright?

24:55.930 --> 25:00.950
[Lucky Gifts]

24:56.460 --> 24:58.750
♪ Dreams made of dazzling starlight ♪

24:59.510 --> 25:01.770
♪ Light up the sky ♪

25:02.880 --> 25:04.620
♪ I run towards your world ♪

25:05.570 --> 25:08.500
♪ With a gaze that mirrors yours ♪

25:09.120 --> 25:16.830
[Lucky Gifts]

25:10.160 --> 25:12.340
♪ The rainbow deep within your heart ♪

25:13.310 --> 25:15.270
♪ Soaring atop the peak ♪

25:16.490 --> 25:18.480
♪ I'm right here by your side ♪

25:19.310 --> 25:22.730
♪ My heart beats in time with yours ♪

25:23.840 --> 25:25.860
♪ Through twists and daring adventures ♪

25:27.070 --> 25:28.740
♪ I'll help you embrace
your transformation ♪

25:29.590 --> 25:31.320
♪ And guard all that makes you
one of a kind ♪

25:31.240 --> 25:32.640
-He added a new one last time.
-Pass the ball!

25:32.640 --> 25:34.200
-Pass.
-What about mental health counseling now?

25:34.200 --> 25:35.350
We already have

25:35.350 --> 25:36.440
a professional
mental health support plan in place.

25:36.440 --> 25:36.720
Don't slack off.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.510
-And we've also brought in a team doctor.
-Pass the ball.

25:38.510 --> 25:39.880
-Quicken your feet!
-Don't worry.

25:39.880 --> 25:41.310
-Our training programs
-Pass.

25:41.310 --> 25:43.370
are tailored to the kids' condition.

25:43.480 --> 25:43.920
Pass the ball!

25:43.920 --> 25:46.160
-We've actually gone over budget.
-Come on, pump your arms!

25:46.160 --> 25:47.240
-Those in the back! Your arms!
-In fact, our training program

25:47.240 --> 25:48.480
-is not bad.
-Pass the ball!

25:48.480 --> 25:48.920
Is that so?

25:48.920 --> 25:50.580
Yes, it's actually very good.

25:51.030 --> 25:51.440
Okay.

25:51.460 --> 25:52.450
-Alright, let's leave it at that for now.
-Okay.

25:52.450 --> 25:53.440
I'll catch up with you later.

25:53.440 --> 25:53.770
Okay.

25:54.400 --> 25:55.310
He's finishing up soon.

25:55.310 --> 25:57.240
Do you want to wait for him in the lounge?

25:57.240 --> 25:58.880
No need. I'll watch him here.

25:58.900 --> 26:01.030
-Let me see who is slacking off.
-Okay.

26:01.480 --> 26:03.680
Why are you carrying so many materials?

26:04.070 --> 26:06.920
These are the upgraded plans
for the youth academy.

26:06.920 --> 26:09.440
He said that besides technique,

26:09.440 --> 26:11.570
mental health is also very important.

26:12.200 --> 26:12.800
Not bad.

26:13.350 --> 26:13.550
Pass the ball.

26:13.550 --> 26:14.950
That's very thoughtful.

26:15.920 --> 26:16.520
By the way,

26:16.590 --> 26:18.160
are you guys preparing

26:18.160 --> 26:19.720
a charity training camp in the mountains?

26:19.720 --> 26:21.650
Yes, I'm going the week after next.

26:21.720 --> 26:22.920
You know Wang Fa.

26:22.920 --> 26:25.310
He's continuing to offer free spots.

26:25.720 --> 26:26.830
He thinks no talent

26:26.830 --> 26:28.000
should be buried.

26:28.830 --> 26:30.640
The only problem is...

26:30.640 --> 26:31.680
that...

26:32.070 --> 26:33.670
I'm under a little pressure.

26:34.200 --> 26:35.310
The budget is too high,

26:35.310 --> 26:37.270
and the financial pressure is immense.

26:37.270 --> 26:38.590
No wonder.

26:38.590 --> 26:40.480
You look like you're going a little bald.

26:40.480 --> 26:41.550
Not at all!

26:41.550 --> 26:43.590
My hairline isn't receding at all.

26:43.920 --> 26:46.850
I'm telling you,
I've had thick hair since I was a kid.

26:47.400 --> 26:48.310
If you call this little hair,

26:48.310 --> 26:49.910
then what about bald people?

26:51.510 --> 26:52.830
Tian...

26:53.110 --> 26:54.640
still hasn't accepted you?

26:55.240 --> 26:56.240
Well...

26:57.550 --> 26:58.720
She said

26:58.720 --> 27:01.250
she'd only let me
take up her time after Wang Fa

27:01.640 --> 27:03.770
and I had run the training school well.

27:03.830 --> 27:04.720
Congratulations.

27:04.720 --> 27:06.980
That means she's finally coming around.

27:07.270 --> 27:08.550
Halfway there, I guess.

27:08.550 --> 27:09.550
But you're right.

27:10.030 --> 27:12.310
If I'm excellent enough, she'll see it.

27:12.880 --> 27:13.510
Right?

27:13.960 --> 27:16.790
I plan to, after everything is done,

27:17.350 --> 27:19.240
take a road trip to relax

27:19.240 --> 27:20.240
and clear my mind.

27:20.790 --> 27:21.720
You? Driving?

27:22.000 --> 27:24.440
Are you sure you won't get lost
once on the road?

27:24.440 --> 27:25.640
-I…
-Don't worry.

27:27.440 --> 27:30.500
I had someone
make a special navigation system for you.

27:32.230 --> 27:33.190
What do you mean?

27:34.720 --> 27:35.450
Just in time.

27:35.680 --> 27:36.540
Mr. Principal,

27:36.640 --> 27:37.480
please work overtime

27:37.480 --> 27:38.940
and finalize these plans.

27:39.030 --> 27:39.960
I can't do it today.

27:39.960 --> 27:41.000
I'll do it tomorrow morning.

27:41.000 --> 27:41.530
Let's go.

27:42.000 --> 27:42.680
Tomorrow?

27:42.680 --> 27:43.170
Wait.

27:43.790 --> 27:45.160
Tomorrow is Saturday!

27:45.720 --> 27:46.720
You are exploiting your employee!

27:46.720 --> 27:47.440
Tell me.

27:47.920 --> 27:50.380
What trick did you pull
with his navigation?

27:51.200 --> 27:53.530
I did some special processing to the voice

27:54.790 --> 27:56.920
and changed it into Wang Tian's voice.

27:57.030 --> 27:58.480
With my sister's sarcasm,

27:58.480 --> 28:00.540
he definitely won't get lost easily.

28:00.880 --> 28:02.540
Use one evil to fight another?

28:03.780 --> 28:05.390
Good idea.

28:14.790 --> 28:16.320
Want to go in and have a look?

28:16.830 --> 28:18.290
Maybe there's a surprise.

28:36.590 --> 28:37.240
Is this...

28:43.500 --> 28:47.250
[Happy Birthday]

28:44.550 --> 28:47.010
Is this the surprise
you were talking about?

28:51.400 --> 28:52.900
[Ms. Lin, Happy birthday]

28:53.590 --> 28:55.160
Surprise!

28:55.480 --> 28:57.080
You startled me.

28:57.480 --> 28:58.510
What brings you here?

28:58.510 --> 29:00.110
To celebrate your birthday.

29:00.920 --> 29:02.320
Did you prepare all this?

29:04.310 --> 29:05.030
Thank you.

29:05.400 --> 29:07.270
Ms. Lin, happy birthday!

29:07.880 --> 29:10.880
We wish you a successful return
to Yongchuan

29:10.880 --> 29:13.440
and hope you
take back everything you lost!

29:14.400 --> 29:15.590
Thank you.

29:15.590 --> 29:18.120
But am I some female version
of Edmond Dantès?

29:18.160 --> 29:19.510
Just kidding.

29:19.510 --> 29:21.000
I grilled all these just now.

29:21.000 --> 29:21.550
I have more ingredients over there.

29:21.550 --> 29:22.880
I'll go grill some more.

29:23.000 --> 29:24.550
Coach, here. Have some milk.

29:24.550 --> 29:25.270
Where is Chen Jianghe?

29:25.270 --> 29:26.880
Didn't you say he was coming with you?

29:26.880 --> 29:28.570
Don't mention him.

29:28.920 --> 29:30.240
He booked the high-speed rail ticket

29:30.240 --> 29:31.640
but was temporarily dragged away
by his teacher.

29:31.640 --> 29:32.310
He had no choice.

29:32.310 --> 29:33.550
The sports university
suddenly had an event,

29:33.550 --> 29:34.270
and they were short on staff.

29:34.270 --> 29:35.550
The whole student union had to go.

29:35.550 --> 29:36.200
But

29:36.200 --> 29:37.550
he told me to wish you

29:37.550 --> 29:38.790
a happy birthday.

29:39.160 --> 29:40.720
I should thank him too.

29:40.720 --> 29:41.520
I understand.

29:42.000 --> 29:44.550
These kids are so outstanding now.

29:44.450 --> 29:47.460
[Ms. Lin, Happy birthday]

29:44.550 --> 29:46.030
Why don't you bribe them

29:46.030 --> 29:48.000
and recruit them to work at your school?

29:48.000 --> 29:49.160
That's a good idea.

29:49.160 --> 29:49.790
No, no.

29:50.270 --> 29:51.220
No need to bribe us at all.

29:51.220 --> 29:52.550
We'd be happy to do that.

29:52.550 --> 29:54.270
Right,
although they aren't here in person,

29:54.270 --> 29:55.790
all their gifts are here.

29:55.890 --> 29:57.850
[Happy Birthday]

29:56.480 --> 29:57.960
This one is from Zhi Hui.

29:57.960 --> 30:00.160
And Yu Ming, Zheng Ren, Jiang...

30:00.590 --> 30:01.520
Right, this one.

30:01.640 --> 30:03.030
This is the most important one.

30:03.030 --> 30:04.720
We wrote this ourselves.

30:07.840 --> 30:08.370
[Ms. Lin: May you live a long and happy life,
stay 18 forever, shine with endless beauty,]

30:08.350 --> 30:09.920
So many idioms?

30:08.390 --> 30:08.920
[be dazzling in every way, enjoy
lasting health and happiness, smile like a flower,]

30:08.940 --> 30:09.110
[stay full of energy,
and have a very happy birthday!]

30:09.110 --> 30:09.510
[By the handsome guys
from Hongjing No. 8 High School]

30:10.160 --> 30:11.200
That's very thoughtful of you.

30:11.200 --> 30:11.800
Thank you.

30:12.720 --> 30:13.920
The beef is here.

30:13.060 --> 30:21.080
[Happy Birthday]

30:14.590 --> 30:15.590
Ms. Lin,

30:15.590 --> 30:16.720
let me tell you, this beef

30:16.720 --> 30:17.680
is very special.

30:18.070 --> 30:20.070
Zheng Feiyang
had it flown in from Shandong.

30:20.070 --> 30:21.510
It's beef from
southwestern Shandong yellow cattle.

30:21.510 --> 30:22.160
It's super tender.

30:22.160 --> 30:23.490
A birthday gift for you.

30:24.070 --> 30:25.400
Tell him thank you.

30:25.400 --> 30:26.660
What is he up to lately?

30:27.160 --> 30:28.960
That kid is doing great.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.960
Whenever he has no classes,
he goes shop-hopping as a vlogger.

30:30.960 --> 30:32.360
He has a ton of followers.

30:33.890 --> 30:39.550
[Happy Birthday]

30:33.960 --> 30:34.960
A vlogger?

30:34.960 --> 30:37.690
Then I have to take a picture of him
for my content.

30:38.680 --> 30:39.920
Sorry I'm late.

30:41.640 --> 30:44.000
Wen Chengye? Aren't you in the US?

30:44.270 --> 30:45.070
Spring break.

30:47.680 --> 30:48.540
Thank you

30:48.640 --> 30:51.970
-To celebrate my birthday, you came...
-You think too much.

30:52.350 --> 30:55.210
I was planning to come back
for spring break anyway.

30:57.000 --> 30:58.510
You haven't changed a bit.

30:58.510 --> 30:59.480
Indeed.

30:59.750 --> 31:02.750
The ugly face of a capitalist.

31:03.200 --> 31:03.960
I just came back,

31:03.960 --> 31:04.960
-and you have started...
-What?

31:04.960 --> 31:06.030
What about it?

31:06.030 --> 31:08.750
Captain, how does
your first year of college feel?

31:08.750 --> 31:09.510
Not bad.

31:09.510 --> 31:11.480
There's not much pressure
at Hongjing Normal University anyway.

31:11.480 --> 31:13.400
We'll see when we start job hunting
after graduation.

31:13.400 --> 31:14.930
Ms. Lin, Coach, have a seat.

31:15.070 --> 31:15.730
Have a seat.

31:26.030 --> 31:26.640
Lu.

31:26.920 --> 31:27.640
Lu?

31:28.920 --> 31:29.590
Boss! Boss!

31:29.590 --> 31:30.790
Have you seen Ms. Lin?

31:31.800 --> 31:33.760
-Lu, long time no see.
-Ms. Lin!

31:33.030 --> 31:36.340
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

31:33.790 --> 31:35.270
I miss you so much!

31:35.270 --> 31:36.590
Happy birthday!

31:36.590 --> 31:37.880
Thank you.

31:37.880 --> 31:39.200
What does the title

31:38.880 --> 31:40.890
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

31:39.200 --> 31:40.600
of your livestream mean?

31:41.440 --> 31:43.480
Skipping work to celebrate a birthday.

31:43.480 --> 31:45.050
Unfollow me if you must?

31:45.350 --> 31:46.110
Keep a low profile.

31:45.400 --> 31:49.980
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

31:46.110 --> 31:48.880
I haven't reached my streaming hours
this month.

31:48.900 --> 31:51.300
Let me just stay live
and rack up some hours.

31:51.350 --> 31:52.950
Do you need me to play for you?

31:53.480 --> 31:55.510
Ms. Lin, your skills are too good.

31:55.530 --> 31:57.800
Everyone in my stream knows I suck.

31:56.690 --> 31:59.310
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

31:58.030 --> 31:59.630
They'd expose me in a second.

32:00.200 --> 32:02.680
Ms. Lin,
are you and Coach doing well lately?

32:03.070 --> 32:05.110
I'll definitely visit you
once I'm done with work.

32:05.110 --> 32:05.680
Okay.

32:07.920 --> 32:09.380
Is this delicious, Coach?

32:10.590 --> 32:11.350
Yes.

32:11.510 --> 32:12.830
Zheng Feiyang sent it.

32:13.240 --> 32:14.690
Let's play together when you come back.

32:14.360 --> 32:17.130
[Skipping Work to Celebrate a Birthday.
Unfollow Me If You Must]

32:14.960 --> 32:15.890
Please carry me!

32:17.240 --> 32:17.960
By the way, Boss.

32:17.960 --> 32:18.960
What is it?

32:19.110 --> 32:22.240
This new gaming chair I bought
is super comfortable.

32:22.270 --> 32:23.650
[Fun-to-Watch Streamer] [Peak King Lu]

32:22.350 --> 32:24.110
You must try it when you're here.

32:24.110 --> 32:24.880
Okay.

32:25.550 --> 32:26.160
Hello.

32:26.160 --> 32:27.640
Can I try it out?

32:27.640 --> 32:29.100
Okay, okay. No problem!

32:29.350 --> 32:30.590
Alright, that's enough.

32:30.590 --> 32:32.640
I'll add everyone to a group chat later.

32:32.640 --> 32:34.510
Just join it,

32:34.510 --> 32:36.550
and then we can hop on a call together.

32:36.550 --> 32:37.440
I'm hanging up now.

32:37.440 --> 32:39.030
Turn off that beauty filter.
It looks terrible.

32:39.030 --> 32:40.270
Okay, no problem.

32:40.720 --> 32:41.250
Bye-bye.

32:42.110 --> 32:43.240
Stop talking and eat up.

32:43.240 --> 32:44.000
-Ms. Lin.
-Okay. Let me see.

32:44.000 --> 32:46.060
I've added them all to the group chat.

32:46.350 --> 32:47.200
I'll go bring out the cake.

32:47.200 --> 32:47.680
I'll connect. You turn it on.

32:47.680 --> 32:48.540
I'll turn it on.

32:56.270 --> 32:57.400
Ms. Lin.

32:58.210 --> 32:59.720
Happy birthday!

32:59.750 --> 33:00.750
Thank you.

33:01.030 --> 33:01.960
It's connected!

33:03.960 --> 33:04.690
Does it work?

33:04.720 --> 33:05.200
Wait a minute.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.600
You need to wait a minute.

33:06.930 --> 33:09.640
Hello, Ms. Lin! Hello, Coach!

33:07.140 --> 33:09.110
[Microphone on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

33:10.880 --> 33:11.750
Coach, can you hear me?

33:11.750 --> 33:12.790
-Stop!
-Can you hear me?

33:12.790 --> 33:13.480
Stop!

33:13.950 --> 33:15.600
[Microphone on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

33:16.280 --> 33:17.010
One at a time.

33:17.030 --> 33:17.680
No rush.

33:17.680 --> 33:18.210
Me first.

33:18.650 --> 33:19.920
Happy birthday, Ms. Lin.

33:19.920 --> 33:20.790
Thank you.

33:20.790 --> 33:22.720
Did you get the southwestern Shandong
yellow cattle beef I sent you?

33:22.720 --> 33:24.440
It was flown to you,

33:24.440 --> 33:25.310
so it's super fresh.

33:25.310 --> 33:27.000
Don't let Qin Ao steal it.

33:27.110 --> 33:29.350
Don't worry, Coach already ate it.

33:29.350 --> 33:30.030
I ate it.

33:30.790 --> 33:32.550
Then I'm relieved.

33:34.550 --> 33:35.400
Ms. Lin,

33:37.640 --> 33:40.640
thank you for helping me
find the courage to face life.

33:41.400 --> 33:42.960
Thank you for being so supportive

33:42.960 --> 33:44.310
when we were at our lowest.

33:44.310 --> 33:46.350
You are a miracle in our lives.

33:47.590 --> 33:48.480
Ms. Lin.

33:48.960 --> 33:50.400
Thank you for being with us.

33:49.830 --> 33:51.010
♪ Time's passing by ♪

33:51.070 --> 33:52.590
I always wish

33:51.760 --> 33:53.800
♪ Nothing remains ♪

33:52.590 --> 33:54.800
I had met you earlier.

33:54.740 --> 33:57.520
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

33:55.350 --> 33:56.550
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

33:57.160 --> 33:58.110
Ms. Lin!

33:58.020 --> 33:59.880
♪ Shadows above ♪

33:58.110 --> 33:59.440
I hope you get prettier and prettier

33:59.440 --> 34:00.500
and stay happy every day.

34:00.500 --> 34:02.430
♪ Rain falls around ♪

34:01.240 --> 34:03.310
Happy birthday!

34:02.790 --> 34:03.770
♪ In your arms ♪

34:03.880 --> 34:04.680
Thank you

34:04.420 --> 34:05.890
♪ We become one ♪

34:04.680 --> 34:07.350
for helping me find the courage
to face difficulties.

34:06.670 --> 34:08.330
♪ Through day and night ♪

34:07.350 --> 34:09.360
I will never forget what you said.

34:09.080 --> 34:10.380
♪ I can see you ♪

34:09.360 --> 34:10.800
Happy birthday to you.

34:11.070 --> 34:12.000
Ms. Lin,

34:12.150 --> 34:14.389
♪ In my eyes ♪

34:12.710 --> 34:13.550
thank you

34:14.480 --> 34:16.440
for helping me
find the most important thing

34:15.250 --> 34:16.719
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

34:16.440 --> 34:17.550
in my life

34:17.560 --> 34:22.770
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

34:17.920 --> 34:20.440
and learn how to cherish it.

34:21.230 --> 34:21.880
Thank you.

34:22.550 --> 34:23.550
Ms. Lin,

34:23.510 --> 34:25.260
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

34:24.760 --> 34:25.800
happy birthday.

34:25.840 --> 34:30.070
[Campus Football Highlights]

34:26.030 --> 34:27.360
Thank you for telling me

34:26.110 --> 34:27.250
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

34:28.159 --> 34:28.940
♪ Wonderful days ♪

34:28.290 --> 34:30.159
that I'm not bad.

34:30.210 --> 34:31.650
♪ Are so close to me ♪

34:32.560 --> 34:35.000
I hope you and Coach have a happy marriage

34:32.610 --> 34:33.780
♪ Memories fly ♪

34:34.040 --> 34:35.880
[Campus Football Highlights]

34:34.679 --> 34:35.929
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

34:35.030 --> 34:36.159
and have a baby soon.

34:36.880 --> 34:37.550
Thank you.

34:36.940 --> 34:42.540
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

34:38.030 --> 34:39.630
Actually, I always imagined how great

34:39.630 --> 34:42.030
it would have been if I had met you
in my freshman year.

34:42.030 --> 34:43.360
Then I wouldn't have been so timid

34:43.360 --> 34:44.360
and lost.

34:44.670 --> 34:45.360
Thank you.

34:45.800 --> 34:48.190
It was you who made me see
my future clearly.

34:48.190 --> 34:49.000
Ms. Lin,

34:48.820 --> 34:50.570
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

34:49.000 --> 34:49.960
happy birthday!

34:50.400 --> 34:53.230
Although I am not the best student
you have had,

34:51.420 --> 34:52.560
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

34:53.230 --> 34:55.440
you are definitely
the best teacher I have ever had.

34:53.469 --> 34:54.389
♪ Wonderful days ♪

34:55.520 --> 34:57.020
♪ Are so close to me ♪

34:55.670 --> 34:56.710
Let's put it this way.

34:56.710 --> 34:57.670
When I see dried radish,

34:57.670 --> 34:58.590
I think of the Robert's Rules of Order

34:57.920 --> 34:59.250
♪ Memories fly ♪

34:58.590 --> 34:59.710
you taught us.

34:59.990 --> 35:01.240
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

35:02.030 --> 35:03.630
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

35:02.250 --> 35:05.470
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

35:03.880 --> 35:05.110
You filled my high school years

35:05.110 --> 35:06.670
with so many wonderful memories.

35:06.180 --> 35:07.930
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

35:08.780 --> 35:09.920
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

35:09.960 --> 35:10.920
Ms. Lin!

35:10.830 --> 35:11.660
♪ Wonderful days ♪

35:11.190 --> 35:15.510
You dida-dida me, I huala-huala you!

35:12.880 --> 35:13.990
♪ Are so close to me ♪

35:14.980 --> 35:16.040
♪ Memories fly ♪

35:15.510 --> 35:17.230
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

35:17.290 --> 35:18.390
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

35:18.360 --> 35:18.960
Brothers,

35:19.190 --> 35:19.840
Let's sing Happy Birthday

35:19.620 --> 35:24.970
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

35:19.840 --> 35:21.000
to Ms. Lin together.

35:21.000 --> 35:21.800
-Okay.
-Okay.

35:24.590 --> 35:25.800
Three, two, one, go!

35:25.800 --> 35:29.700
Happy birthday to you.

35:29.730 --> 35:33.590
Happy birthday to you.

36:01.030 --> 36:06.590
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

36:07.500 --> 36:11.570
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

36:14.000 --> 36:18.620
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

36:16.480 --> 36:17.610
-Hurry up!
-Coming.

36:18.360 --> 36:19.560
Take a picture for me.

36:19.860 --> 36:25.290
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

36:21.770 --> 36:27.060
[Graduation Ceremony]

36:26.770 --> 36:32.180
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

36:27.540 --> 36:33.990
[Graduation Season—Forever Young]

36:33.500 --> 36:37.940
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

36:39.700 --> 36:44.880
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

36:45.520 --> 36:50.690
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

36:51.520 --> 36:57.480
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

36:58.130 --> 37:03.900
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

37:04.580 --> 37:10.190
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

37:11.040 --> 37:16.280
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

37:18.030 --> 37:23.190
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

37:24.220 --> 37:29.670
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

37:30.740 --> 37:36.350
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

37:37.400 --> 37:42.640
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

37:55.360 --> 37:58.510
[Wen Chengye]

38:01.690 --> 38:06.410
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

38:04.460 --> 38:07.620
[Wen Chengye] [Fu Xinshu]

38:07.320 --> 38:11.960
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

38:13.720 --> 38:18.900
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

38:19.540 --> 38:26.100
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

38:28.670 --> 38:34.490
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

38:28.800 --> 38:34.700
[Graduation Ceremony]

38:35.280 --> 38:41.050
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

38:41.740 --> 38:47.350
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

38:48.190 --> 38:53.430
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

38:53.960 --> 38:55.170
Stand there. Don't move.

38:55.170 --> 39:00.340
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

39:01.360 --> 39:06.820
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

39:02.550 --> 39:03.190
What are you doing?

39:03.190 --> 39:04.110
You guys are the noisiest.

39:04.110 --> 39:05.000
-Be careful.
-Exactly.

39:05.000 --> 39:06.000
You guys are the noisiest.

39:06.000 --> 39:07.920
-They are the noisiest.
-Come on!

39:07.880 --> 39:13.240
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

39:07.920 --> 39:09.670
We can't even find you!

39:09.670 --> 39:11.190
Let's take a group photo
of our football team.

39:11.190 --> 39:12.440
Come on.

39:12.440 --> 39:13.800
I'll hold it. Take your time.

39:13.800 --> 39:14.480
Do you know how to do it?

39:14.480 --> 39:14.880
Get down!

39:14.540 --> 39:19.540
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

39:16.190 --> 39:18.510
-Get down, get down.
-Get down.

39:18.510 --> 39:19.510
Jianghe is out of the frame.

39:19.510 --> 39:20.880
-Seriously.
-Jianghe, Jianghe.

39:20.880 --> 39:22.440
-Okay.
-There's a bee here!

39:21.470 --> 39:25.450
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

39:23.840 --> 39:24.480
Come on.

39:24.480 --> 39:26.810
Hurry up. You're actually afraid of this?

39:27.760 --> 39:35.360
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

39:28.550 --> 39:32.960
-Happy graduation!
-Happy graduation!

39:32.960 --> 39:33.880
Hold on, hold on.

39:33.880 --> 39:35.480
-For the graduation…
-Where are Ms. Lin and Coach?

39:35.480 --> 39:36.190
They're not here yet?

39:36.190 --> 39:37.280
They're not here yet?

39:37.280 --> 39:38.360
Just call them.

39:38.360 --> 39:39.190
Call them.

39:39.190 --> 39:40.070
Make a video call.

39:40.070 --> 39:40.960
A video call.

39:47.480 --> 39:49.360
-Coach!
-Coach!

39:52.920 --> 39:53.960
Come on, Coach, what time is it?

39:53.960 --> 39:55.290
Why aren't you here yet?

39:56.230 --> 39:56.880
Got it.

40:00.670 --> 40:01.920
To my students.

40:04.150 --> 40:06.960
I joined Hongjing No. 8 High School
last year.

40:08.070 --> 40:10.630
When I stood at the door
of the Sports Equipment Room,

40:08.710 --> 40:12.070
[Sports Equipment Room]

40:11.360 --> 40:12.550
I never thought

40:13.190 --> 40:15.030
that I would become so deeply involved

40:15.030 --> 40:17.360
in other people's journeys through life.

40:23.440 --> 40:26.950
Back then, trapped by my own painful fate,

40:27.550 --> 40:30.540
I knew that the hardest thing to overcome

40:30.710 --> 40:32.970
was the struggle within one's own heart.

40:34.070 --> 40:35.590
Like everyone else,

40:36.080 --> 40:39.550
I longed to witness
an unstoppable dark horse rise.

40:40.150 --> 40:42.560
I hoped to find, in your stories,

40:42.670 --> 40:45.000
the meaning
that would help me keep going.

40:47.400 --> 40:48.360
Later,

40:49.030 --> 40:50.230
I realized

40:51.590 --> 40:53.510
that the hardest part of life

40:53.510 --> 40:56.440
is not the momentary decision
to set out on a journey,

40:56.630 --> 41:00.360
but the lasting willpower needed
to keep climbing toward the peak.

41:00.480 --> 41:01.700
[Feng Suo]
[Play football with the brothers]

41:01.190 --> 41:02.590
The greatest pain

41:03.000 --> 41:05.550
is not gritting your teeth
after falling off a cliff,

41:04.020 --> 41:04.530
[But what I want most in the end]

41:04.550 --> 41:05.260
[is to win the championship with the guys]
[Yu Ming]

41:06.320 --> 41:07.960
but facing yourself and

41:07.360 --> 41:08.500
[Win the championship]
[Chen Jianghe]

41:08.760 --> 41:10.920
making the choice that stays true
to your conscience.

41:10.450 --> 41:11.800
[Qin Ao]
[I want to win the championship]

41:14.670 --> 41:15.760
Education

41:16.360 --> 41:18.550
has never been about me teaching you.

41:19.360 --> 41:21.440
It has always been about us,
teachers and students,

41:21.440 --> 41:22.710
helping each other

41:23.440 --> 41:25.000
and growing together.

41:24.370 --> 41:26.550
[1 day until the evil monthly exam]

41:26.960 --> 41:28.370
The Olympic spirit

41:28.670 --> 41:33.230
is about being faster,
higher, and stronger.

41:34.400 --> 41:36.480
And you have taught me

41:37.070 --> 41:38.930
that through physical training

41:39.110 --> 41:41.190
and the pursuit of the limits
of willpower,

41:41.190 --> 41:43.000
the boundaries of the soul

41:43.280 --> 41:45.030
can expand and grow wider

41:45.630 --> 41:46.960
amid hardship.

41:50.110 --> 41:51.440
Adults always say

41:52.030 --> 41:54.090
that when you grow up, you will find

41:54.320 --> 41:57.150
the road ahead becoming wider and wider.

41:58.480 --> 42:00.150
But unease and confusion,

42:00.670 --> 42:02.760
pain and hesitation,

42:02.760 --> 42:04.150
extreme hardships,

42:04.150 --> 42:05.590
and difficult choices

42:06.070 --> 42:07.510
have always been narrow paths

42:07.510 --> 42:09.970
that few people
ever manage to walk through.

42:11.510 --> 42:13.030
Real life

42:13.550 --> 42:15.150
is bitter and long.

42:15.670 --> 42:17.120
Persevering to the end

42:17.510 --> 42:19.660
may not always lead to a bright future.

42:21.440 --> 42:22.460
So,

42:22.880 --> 42:23.840
it's okay

42:24.280 --> 42:25.760
to run away.

42:32.960 --> 42:35.100
But I have always hoped that you would

42:35.230 --> 42:38.000
have free will and independent minds.

42:38.480 --> 42:40.400
I hope you will learn how to live,

42:40.400 --> 42:42.130
come to terms with yourselves,

42:42.260 --> 42:43.930
discover what you love,

42:44.080 --> 42:45.940
and have the courage to pursue it.

42:46.550 --> 42:48.480
I hope you will always fight

42:48.480 --> 42:50.680
against the timid side of human nature,

42:51.510 --> 42:52.920
live with courage,

42:53.510 --> 42:54.590
and always

42:55.150 --> 42:57.150
give me the strength to seek understanding

42:57.150 --> 42:58.800
even in moments of despair.

43:02.540 --> 43:03.530
[Strive to ensure
that the people experience]

43:03.560 --> 43:04.910
[fairness and justice
in every judicial case.]

43:04.030 --> 43:05.760
And more than anything, I hope

43:06.670 --> 43:08.150
that I, too,

43:08.150 --> 43:09.960
can become

43:09.960 --> 43:11.960
the person I aspire to be.

43:14.030 --> 43:15.550
Today, you no longer

43:15.580 --> 43:18.060
need to read these meaningless words.

43:18.800 --> 43:20.360
Yet, as you graduate,

43:20.710 --> 43:23.670
I still want to offer my blessings
for the journey ahead,

43:23.670 --> 43:25.880
hoping that no matter how narrow
the road may seem,

43:25.880 --> 43:27.880
you will eventually find the light.

